name: Nifty Royale X James Ramirez Resilience

metadata.description: This mask series creates physical representations of experiences. Resilience is born through adversity and our character is a tapestry of experiences. Through thick and thin we push on, adding new dents, welds, and details to our masks. Mask Collection 2: Sculpted in virtual reality, rendered in C4D using Octane and finished in After Effects.
metadata.name: Resilience - Gold

attributes.value: James Ramirez is a creative based in Los Angeles. Working in the motion design industry he has worked on title sequences for films, tv, and video games. From James Bond, Stranger Than Fiction to Into the Spider-verse. In his personal work he explores and experiments to present stories in different mediums and styles.
